autocompletesText: Suggests relevant options as the user types.
badgesText: A small value indicator that can be overlaid on another object.
bottomSheetsText: A large interactive panel primarily for mobile devices.
buttonGroupsText: A groupable on/off toggle for enabling and disabling options.
buttonsAndIndicatorsText: An interaction button with a range of presentation options.
buttonsText: Buttons, toggles, status and progress indicators
cardsText: A styled container for pieces of itemized content.
checkboxesText: Captures boolean input with an optional indeterminate mode.
chipsText: Presents a list of items as a set of small, tactile entities.
dataIteratorsText: Allows the user to configure how tabular data is displayed.
dataTablesText: A configurable component for displaying tabular data
datePickersText: Capture dates, agnostic about their internal representation.
dialogsText: A configurable modal that displays dynamic content.
dividersText: A vertical or horizontal visual divider.
expansionPanelsText: A container which can be expanded to reveal more content.
formsText: Controls that collect and validate user input.
inputsText: Enables native inputs to be used within a Form field
layoutText: Essential building blocks for presenting your content.
menusText: A floating panel of nestable options.
modalsText: Floating components that can be dynamically shown or hidden.
navigationDrawersText: A container for content that is fixed to one side of the screen.
navigationText: Menus, navigation drawers and toolbars that organize your content
radiosText: Allow the user to select one option from a group.
selectsText: Allow the user to select one or more options using a dropdown.
slideTogglesText: Captures boolean values as a clickable and draggable switch.
slidersText: Allows the user to input a value by dragging along a slider.
snackbarsText: Displays short actionable messages as an uninvasive alert.
steppersText: Presents content as steps through which to progress.
tablesText: Tools for displaying and interacting with tabular data.
tabsText: Only presents one view at a time from a provided set of views.
toolbarsText: A container for top-level titles and controls.
tooltipsText: Displays floating content when an object is hovered.
treeviewText: Presents hierarchical content as an expandable tree
